quick-notes-description =
    A simple sticky-note widget for the FreeSynergy desktop.

    Lets you jot down short text snippets that persist across sessions. Notes are stored
    locally in the Node database. Supports plain text and optional Markdown rendering.
    Multiple Quick Notes widgets can coexist on the same desktop layout — each with its
    own independent content.

quick-notes-features =
    - Plain text and Markdown rendering modes
    - Notes persist across sessions (stored in Node database)
    - Multiple independent notes on one desktop
    - Resizable from 2x2 to 6x6 grid slots
    - No external dependencies
